---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="About | Bitcoin Strategi"
  description="Mission, principles, and approach behind Bitcoin Strategi."
>
  <section class="hero section reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">[ About the desk ]</p>
    <h1>We publish Bitcoin strategy for people who value structure over hype.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Bitcoin Strategi is an independent education project focused on practical
      execution quality: risk sizing, behavior rules, and cycle-aware planning.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="grid-three section reveal">
    <article class="panel feature-panel">
      <p class="pill">Mission</p>
      <h2>Turn complexity into clear actions.</h2>
      <p>
        We simplify market and protocol topics into practical decisions you can
        execute consistently.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel feature-panel">
      <p class="pill">Editorial rule</p>
      <h2>No sensationalism.</h2>
      <p>
        No panic headlines, no blind optimism. We optimize for long-term decision
        quality and realistic risk framing.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel feature-panel">
      <p class="pill">Outcome</p>
      <h2>Better behavior under pressure.</h2>
      <p>
        When markets move fast, a robust process beats short-term opinion every
        time.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="grid-two section reveal">
    <article class="panel depth-panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">[ Framework ]</p>
      <h2>How we evaluate every strategy idea</h2>
      <ul class="bullet-list">
        <li>Can it survive a severe drawdown?</li>
        <li>Can you execute it without daily stress?</li>
        <li>Does it improve your downside profile?</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="panel depth-panel accent-panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">[ Contact ]</p>
      <h2>Need a second pair of eyes on your setup?</h2>
      <p>
        We can help you pressure-test your framework and make it operational.
      </p>
      <div class="inline-actions">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
